channel.title: Ekstrak - 202X [DnB]
channel.description:
![image|500x500](upload://2qUsROwx6OLw4OaPD8gjW3COcic.jpeg)
[Spotify Link](https://open.spotify.com/album/3eYqdsCZcGZOCV0htm3RTx?si=NtskHj6pSHuLJ8tiVM8EJw) [SoundCloud Link (Shorter)](https://soundcloud.com/xtrk/202x) [iTunes Link](https://itunes.apple.com/us/artist/ekstrak/208883275?ign-gact=1) [YouTube Link](https://youtu.be/muVIXrCP7fg)
It’s safe to say that I am proud with this track. So proud that I might be posting a remixing competition of this song. Let me know if this is a good idea.
This single project took me two months to make. It has gone to many major changes, but I decided that this is the best one out of them all. From the producers of Atari and Stardust, I bring you 202X.
